description:
MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

We are continuing work on our lava can factory today. We manage to get it up and running, although just barely.

Note: Even though I was having problems at the end of the episode, these have all been fixed by now.
